# Project Rules for SONDR

## Testing with XcodeBuildMCP
When testing with XcodeBuildMCP:
- Build, install, and launch the app on the simulator
- Tell the user what to click/navigate to test the changes
- Do not take screenshots or verify visually - the user will test manually
- Wait for user feedback before proceeding

## File Locations
- All project-specific files (plans, documentation, etc.) must be saved in the project directory: `/Users/kmaha/Dev/SONDR_V1/.cursor/` or subdirectories within the project
- Never save project-specific files to `/Users/kmaha/.cursor/` (home directory) - that is for global Cursor configuration only
- When creating plans, save them to `.cursor/plans/` within the project directory
